---
/**
 * Use Cases section showcasing real-world applications
 */
---

<section class="use-cases-section">
  <h2 class="section-title">Use Cases</h2>
  <p class="section-subtitle">Privacy for every Web3 application</p>

  <div class="cases-grid">
    <a href="/guides/solver-integration/" class="case-card">
      <div class="case-icon">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
          <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
          <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
          <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="case-title">DAO Governance</h3>
      <p class="case-desc">Private voting and treasury management without revealing member balances</p>
    </a>

    <a href="/concepts/viewing-key/" class="case-card">
      <div class="case-icon">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
          <path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="case-title">Treasury Operations</h3>
      <p class="case-desc">Shield institutional transfers while maintaining audit compliance</p>
    </a>

    <a href="/concepts/privacy-levels/" class="case-card">
      <div class="case-icon">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"></line>
          <path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="case-title">DEX Privacy</h3>
      <p class="case-desc">Private swaps across any chain without front-running exposure</p>
    </a>

    <a href="/concepts/stealth-address/" class="case-card">
      <div class="case-icon">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <rect x="1" y="4" width="22" height="16" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
          <line x1="1" y1="10" x2="23" y2="10"></line>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="case-title">Payments</h3>
      <p class="case-desc">Send and receive privately with stealth addresses</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .use-cases-section {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.03) 0%, transparent 100%);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-white);
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-3);
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
  }

  .cases-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .case-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .case-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.08);
    border-color: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
  }

  .case-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    color: #a78bfa;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .case-title {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--sl-color-white);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .case-desc {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-3);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
    text-align: left;
  }

  /* Light theme */
  :root[data-theme='light'] .section-title {
    color: var(--sl-color-black);
  }

  :root[data-theme='light'] .case-card {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
    border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  :root[data-theme='light'] .case-card:hover {
    background: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.05);
    border-color: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.2);
  }

  :root[data-theme='light'] .case-icon {
    background: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.1);
    color: #7c3aed;
  }

  :root[data-theme='light'] .case-title {
    color: var(--sl-color-black);
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .cases-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
